➜王健林旗下AMC院线拟申请破产，“现金可能很快用完”
http://www.sohu.com/a/424482939_260616	311
<div id="sohuplayer">
<script type="text/javascript" src="//tv.sohu.com/upload/swf/showVrsPlayer.js"></script>
